text: Tadeusz Górczyk (16 October 1961 – 21 December 2020) was a Polish politician. He was a member of the Sejm from 1991 to 1993. He was a member of the Centre Agreement. Górczyk was born in Jasło, Poland. Górczyk died on 21 December 2020 at the age of 59. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish politicians
